AUDIO: 'look. Listen, I\'m I know I lied about my age. I\'m sorry, but the second I saw your profile and I I I the painting with the tulips, you\'re just like the most gorgeous girl ever, and you\'re such an unbelievably talented artist. Do you think you can just give me like one'

