AUDIO: 'domains before 2030. Last I checked, that\'s 5 years away. Since the golden age of Athens, the West has argued that education isn\'t just about acquiring knowledge. It\'s about training the mind'

[07:20] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'to form the human soul for virtue, for greatness. Today, it\'s not even about acquiring knowledge or even job skills. But the Ivy\'s and Western universities at all levels have not seemed to notice yet. Colombia suspendedly citing'

