VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'rise that may yet save the world. Lee may have instinctively known and guessed that Western universities like Colombia are but empty simulations of the human education they once purported to offer.'

[11:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'But he is dead wrong that the future of humanity belongs to Cluly, to those who can cheat at everything. The future of humanity belongs to the new privileged class. I don\'t mean white boys at Yale.'

[11:24] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Those days are gone. The new privileged class is the small remnant of children whose parents and teachers have made the radical decision to opt out of the AI revolution during those critical years'

[11:37] [scene:talk]
